〈'''Save the Day'''〉是美國女歌手[[瑪麗亞·凱莉|瑪麗亞·凱莉]]在2020年8月21日發行的單曲<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariah Carey announces ''The Rarities'' album|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/mariah-carey-announces-the-rarities-album-featuring-unreleased-collaboration-with-lauryn-hill__30788/|access-date=2020-08-21|website=www.officialcharts.com|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821165644/https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/mariah-carey-announces-the-rarities-album-featuring-unreleased-collaboration-with-lauryn-hill__30788/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。〈Save the Day〉是凱莉第八張[[合輯|合輯]]《[[藏愛|藏愛]]》的首張單曲，由[[哥倫比亞唱片|哥倫比亞唱片]]及{{Internal link helper/en|Legacy唱片|Legacy Recordings}}發行<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-19|title=Mariah Carey Handpicks Favorites From Her Vault for ''The Rarities'' Album, Coming Friday, October 2|url=https://legacyrecordings.com/2020/08/19/mariah-carey-handpicks-favorites-from-her-vault-for-the-rarities-album-coming-friday-october-2/|access-date=2020-08-21|website=Legacy Recordings|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902151711/https://legacyrecordings.com/2020/08/19/mariah-carey-handpicks-favorites-from-her-vault-for-the-rarities-album-coming-friday-october-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，瑪麗亞·凱莉、[[杰梅因·杜普里|杰梅因·杜普里]]、{{Internal link helper/en|James "Big Jim" Wright|Sounds of Blackness}}、{{Internal link helper/en|Charles Fox|Charles Fox}}及{{Internal link helper/en|Norman Gimbel|Norman Gimbel}}作詞編曲。由瑪麗亞·凱莉及杰梅因·杜普里監製<ref>{{cite web|url=https://listen.tidal.com/album/152222466/credits|title=Save the Day (2020) - Credits|publisher=[[TIDAL|TIDAL]]|accessdate=August 23, 2020|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902151701/https://listen.tidal.com/album/152222466/credits|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/2YjzMFVEK0gWVc95yJaCAe|title=Save the Day (2020)|publisher=[[Spotify|Spotify]]|accessdate=August 23, 2020|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830153638/https://open.spotify.com/album/2YjzMFVEK0gWVc95yJaCAe|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pandora.com/artist/credits/mariah-carey/save-the-day-2020-single/save-the-day-2020/TRnwdj9ZzkldpvP|title=Save the Day (2020) by Mariah Carey - Pandora|publisher=[[Pandora_Radio|Pandora]]|accessdate=August 23, 2020|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902151701/https://www.pandora.com/artist/credits/mariah-carey/save-the-day-2020-single/save-the-day-2020/TRnwdj9ZzkldpvP|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariah Carey with Lauryn Hill - Save the Day|url=https://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-with-Lauryn-Hill-Save-The-Day/release/15798947|access-date=2020-08-23|website=Discogs|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902151701/https://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-with-Lauryn-Hill-Save-The-Day/release/15798947|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dupri">{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/mariah-carey-shares-new-song-save-the-day-featuring-lauryn-hill-2735064%3famp|title=Mariah Carey shares new song 'Save the Day' featuring Lauryn Hill|publisher=[[NME|NME]]|last=Lavin|first=Will|date=August 22, 2020|accessdate=August 23, 2020|quote=The track is produced by Jermaine Dupri.|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824054612/https://www.nme.com/news/music/mariah-carey-shares-new-song-save-the-day-featuring-lauryn-hill-2735064?amp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

歌曲[[取樣_(音樂)|採樣]]自美國女歌手[[勞琳·希爾|勞琳·希爾]]所屬組合[[難民營樂隊|難民營樂隊]]的〈{{le|Killing Me Softly with His Song|Killing Me Softly with His Song}}〉<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariah Carey with Lauryn Hill - Save the Day|url=https://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-with-Lauryn-Hill-Save-The-Day/release/15798947|access-date=2020-08-21|website=Discogs|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902151701/https://www.discogs.com/Mariah-Carey-with-Lauryn-Hill-Save-The-Day/release/15798947|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
[[瑪麗亞·凱莉|瑪麗亞·凱莉]]和她的長期音樂拍擋[[杰梅因·杜普里|杰梅因·杜普里]]於2011年開始製作此曲。凱莉原意希望集合其他音樂家例如[[玛丽·布莱姬|玛丽·布莱姬]]及[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒·斯威夫特]]合唱<ref name=OhNicki/>，把此曲作為[[公益歌曲|公益歌曲]]。歌曲靈感來自美國公益組織{{Internal link helper/en|Points of Light|Points of Light}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Jermaine Dupri and Mariah Carey to Create Musical Collaboration to Celebrate the Power of People to Make Change in the World|url=http://www.twitlonger.com/show/8pjq8c|date=2011-02-10|access-date=2020-08-30|website=Twitlonger|archive-date=2011-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110216011510/http://www.twitlonger.com/show/8pjq8c|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
2011年3月，瑪麗亞·凱莉的發言人表示，〈Save the Day〉是為凱莉第十四張錄音室專輯《{{Internal link helper/en|聽我...歌情萬種|Me. I Am Mariah... The Elusive Chanteuse}}》而寫的，版權收益將會全數捐出予人權組織。發言人指凱莉將繼續把她的時間及金錢捐贈給國內外的許多組織<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariah Carey 'Embarrassed' Over Gadhafi-Linked Concert|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/472771/mariah-carey-embarrassed-over-gadhafi-linked-concert|date=2011-03-03|access-date=2020-08-30|website=Billboard|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710051433/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/472771/mariah-carey-embarrassed-over-gadhafi-linked-concert|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年2月11日，凱莉於自己的[[推特|推特]]賬戶表示，這首歌「由於非常特殊的原因」而處於製作停滯狀態，將不日公開<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariah Carey - Twitter|url=https://twitter.com/MariahCarey/status/168359456986505216?s=20|access-date=2020-08-30|website=Twitter}}</ref>。

==宣傳及發行==
2020年8月19日，瑪麗亞·凱莉宣佈〈Save the Day〉將以第八張[[合輯|合輯]]《[[藏愛|藏愛]]》首張單曲的身份發行<ref name=gma>{{cite news |url=https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/mariah-carey-shares-details-upcoming-album-fans-72466528 |title=Mariah Carey shares details about her upcoming album: 'This one is for you, my fans' |publisher=Good Morning America |last=FitzPatrick |first=Hayley |date=August 19, 2020 |accessdate=August 19, 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820103051/https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/mariah-carey-shares-details-upcoming-album-fans-72466528 |archivedate=2020-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。發行前一天，凱莉邀請粉絲、記者及朋友<ref name=OhBillboard/>舉行私人[[Zoom|Zoom]]視像聆聽派對<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mariah Carey premieres new single ‘Save the Day’ via private Zoom party|url=https://e-radio.us/mariah-carey-premieres-new-single-save-the-day-via-private-zoom-party/|date=2020-08-20|access-date=2020-08-30|website=e-Radio.us|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902151808/https://e-radio.us/mariah-carey-premieres-new-single-save-the-day-via-private-zoom-party/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凱莉於聆聽派對上表示，發行歌曲時正值[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]於全球大流行，她認為〈Save the Day〉的歌詞剛好符合時局，希望大家能夠抱有希望並團結一致<ref name=OhNicki>{{cite web |last1=Lusk |first1=Darian |title=The real meaning behind Mariah Carey's Save the Day |url=https://www.nickiswift.com/238978/the-real-meaning-behind-mariah-careys-save-the-day/?utm_campaign=clip |website=NickiSwift.com |accessdate=2020-09-03 |date=2020-08-22}}</ref>。凱莉又指自己是[[取樣_(音樂)|採樣]]原曲《{{Internal link helper/en|Killing Me Softly with His Song|Killing Me Softly with His Song}}》的粉絲。凱莉又讚賞[[劳琳·希尔|勞琳·希爾]]，認為她是一位出色的藝人，並感謝希爾批准她採樣<ref name=OhBillboard/>。

==評價==
《Billboard》認為發行歌曲時正值[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]肆虐，凱莉的歌詞能傳達及時信息，聲線「發自內心情感，令人感動」。再加上凱莉的經典高音、[[劳琳·希尔|勞琳·希爾]]的聲線以及[[杰梅因·杜普里|傑梅因·杜普里]]的音樂，給予〈Save the Day〉高度評價<ref name=OhBillboard>{{cite web |title=Mariah Carey's Ms. Lauryn Hill Collab 'Save the Day' Is Here: Stream It Now |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9437856/mariah-carey-save-the-day-lauryn-hill |website=Billboard |accessdate=2020-09-03 |date=2020-08-21 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902085403/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9437856/mariah-carey-save-the-day-lauryn-hill |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

